KineticFire Labs
	  Project site:  https://github.com/kineticfire-labs/git-conventional-commits-hooks



All commands executed from 'git-hooks/client/' as follows:

    Run:

        Run 'commit-msg':
            bb go:commit

    Test:

        Test all:
            bb test

        Test 'commit-msg':
            bb test:commit 

    Build uberscript:

        Build uberscript for all:
            bb uber

        Build uberscript for 'commit-msg':
            bb uber:commit


Carve information:
   - https://github.com/borkdude/carve                                                                        
   - To get the latest SHA:
      git ls-remote https://github.com/borkdude/carve.git refs/heads/master
